metadata.title: DPM/FM Dar reaffirms Pakistanâ€™s commitment to further strengthening cooperation with EU

content.article_body:
ISLAMABAD, Oct 20 (APP): Deputy Prime Minister/Foreign Minister Senator Mohammad Ishaq Dar, on Monday, reaffirmed Pakistan's commitment to further deepening Pakistan-EU cooperation, including under the GSP+ framework.

The DPM/FM received and congratulated the newly appointed EU Ambassador to Pakistan Raimundas Karoblis," Foreign Office Spokesperson said in a press release.

Recent regional and international developments were also discussed during the meeting.
